comments.body:
I think it might be good to approach this from the perspective of what we need day-to-day, vs. what would be nice to have, vs. what we might expect at crunch times (e.g., week before production deploy).  Something like:

* All the time:
   * Available to answer questions on Slack or email
   * Attend demos approx. every 2 weeks
* Nice to have:
   * Attend weekly meeting on Monday or Friday
* Crunch time:
   * Attend daily standup
